'''杨清培'''（{{bd|1989年}}<ref>{{Cite web|title=Yang Qingpei in China kills parents and 17 neighbours in Yunnan Province|url=http://www.news.com.au/lifestyle/real-life/wtf/yang-qingpei-in-china-kills-parents-and-17-neighbours-in-yunnan-province/news-story/98c9b4e91f58c5e082467a3832716f2e|accessdate=|author=<!--Staff writer(s); no by-line.-->|date=|work=news.com.au|publisher=|quote=|archive-date=2019-04-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190407203533/https://www.news.com.au/lifestyle/real-life/wtf/yang-qingpei-in-china-kills-parents-and-17-neighbours-in-yunnan-province/news-story/98c9b4e91f58c5e082467a3832716f2e|dead-url=no}}</ref> ），中国杀人犯，被控于2016年9月29日在[[云南省|云南省]][[曲靖市|曲靖市]][[会泽县|会泽县]][[待补镇|待补镇]]野马村杀害19人。杨清培在向父母要钱时与父母发生争执，将父母杀害，然后又杀死了6户邻居的17口人以掩盖罪行，受害者年龄从3岁到72岁不等。杨清培于次日在[[昆明市|昆明市]]被捕。<ref>{{Cite web|title=Man 'kills 17 to hide parents' murder'|url=https://www.bbc.com/news/world-asia-37521650|date=30 September 2016|publisher=|access-date=2020-08-17|archive-date=2020-11-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201108091809/https://www.bbc.com/news/world-asia-37521650|dead-url=no}}</ref>2017年7月28日，杨清培被判处死刑。<ref>{{Cite web|title=Man who killed parents and then 17 neighbours to cover it up given death penalty in China|url=https://news.sky.com/story/man-who-killed-parents-and-then-17-neighbours-to-cover-it-up-given-death-penalty-in-china-10964998|publisher=|access-date=2020-08-17|archive-date=2020-11-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201111210832/https://news.sky.com/story/man-who-killed-parents-and-then-17-neighbours-to-cover-it-up-given-death-penalty-in-china-10964998|dead-url=no}}</ref>

